    <h1>Referral Marketing</h1>
    <p class="description">A customer acquisition strategy that turns existing buyers into brand advocates. When done right, referral programs deliver <strong>higher-converting, lower-CAC customers</strong> than almost any paid channel.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
